---
// 成果保証システムの説明セクション
---

<section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-green-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        成果保証の仕組み
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        リスクなしで確実な成果を提供する、業界唯一の保証システム
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 2段階の保証システム -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- 第1段階：技術保証 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 p-3 rounded-full mr-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">第1段階：技術保証（3ヶ月）</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">モバイル：PageSpeed Insights 85点以上</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">デスクトップ：PageSpeed Insights 93点以上</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Core Web Vitals全指標で「良好」評価</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-red-800 mb-2">未達成時の対応</h4>
          <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">→ 3ヶ月分の月額料金50%返金</p>
          <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">→ 追加1ヶ月の無料改善サポート</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 第2段階：ビジネス成果保証 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 border-l-4 border-green-500">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div class="bg-green-100 p-3 rounded-full mr-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">第2段階：ビジネス成果保証（6ヶ月）</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">サイト滞在時間15%向上</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">直帰率10%改善</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">お問い合わせ数20%増加</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">ページビュー15%増加</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-orange-50 border border-orange-200 rounded-lg p-4">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-orange-800 mb-2">未達成時の対応</h4>
          <p class="text-orange-700 text-sm">→ 4-6ヶ月目の月額料金30%返金</p>
          <p class="text-orange-700 text-sm">→ 改善提案レポート（5万円相当）無料提供</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 6ヶ月後の選択肢 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-8">6ヶ月後の3つの選択肢</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center p-6 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-lg">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">年契約（10%OFF）</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">成果を実感した方にお得な年契約プラン</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-lg">
          <div class="bg-green-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">月契約継続</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">柔軟性を重視する方の月契約プラン</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6 border-2 border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
          <div class="bg-gray-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-gray-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">解約</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600">成果が不十分な場合の解約オプション</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
